# OG Image Generator — local environment
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value(s) below.
# `.env.local` is git-ignored, so your real key never gets committed.

# Turns ON the real AI art direction (the "Describe this post" → Generate flow).
# With a key, suggestions come from Claude reasoning over the icon/template
# library + featured examples. Without it, the app still works — it falls back
# to a keyword match over the seed icons.
#
# Get a key: https://console.anthropic.com → Settings → API keys → "Create key".
# It starts with "sk-ant-". Paste it after the = below (no quotes), then restart
# `pnpm dev`.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Supabase (asset library, persistence, auth) ---
# From your project's dashboard → Project Settings → API. The URL and
# publishable key are public (safe in the browser); the secret key is NOT — it
# stays server-side only. The app runs without these (bundled seed data); they
# turn on the shared backend.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY=
